================================================================================================================================
If you need to know the directory you are working on, use the following command:
alisson@devops:~/.ssh$ pwd
/home/alisson/.ssh
And if you want to go to the previous directory again, use the command cd using
two dots (..):
alisson@devops:~/.ssh$ cd ..
alisson@devops:~$ pwd
/home/alisson
